  <brief_title>Investigation of Cognitive Function Before and After Induced Ventricular Fibrillation in Electrophysiological (EP) Study</brief_title>
  <official_title>Change of EEG Activity and Cerebral Circulation During Induced Ventricular Fibrillation and Investigation of Cognitive Function Before and After Induced Ventricular Fibrillation in EP Study</official_title>
  <sponsors>
