  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Age &gt; 18 years

          -  Positive agreement

          -  EPS for primary and secondary prophylaxis of a malignant ventricular tachyarrhythmia:

               -  primary prophylaxis: Brugada syndrome, long QT syndrome, cardiomyopathy, short QT
                  syndrome

               -  secondary prophylaxis: Multicenter Automatic Defibrillator Implantation Trial
                  (MADIT) criteria, syncope, documented ventricular tachycardia

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Severe neurological deficit

          -  Cardiopulmonary resuscitation
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
